          <text id="/data/person/kym_message/kym_message_note:label">
            <value>The Health Card is a national program that was adopted by the government of Zanzibar. It means that every Zanzibari should be registered, have a Health Card, and use it every time they receive services at a health facility. This card collects all medical information that the patient has received, enabling access to essential information for future treatments. Additionally, it enables the government to track the usage of health resources such as medical equipment and medicines, thus helping to plan and budget effectively to improve health services. The Health Card also enhances transparency and efficiency in the collection of health data, providing better health services that are essential for the development of citizens and the health sector as a whole.</value>
          </text>
